Useful fabrication related notes (cheatsheet)
=============================================

Environmental variables::

    export FAB_MAKEFILE_INCLUDE_PATH=/turnkey/private/fab/contrib
    export FAB_PLAN_INCLUDE_PATH=/turnkey/fab/common-plans
    export FAB_PATH=/turnkey/fab
    export FAB_POOL_PATH=/turnkey/fab/pools/rocky2
    export O=build


Making a product (licop ready)::

    BATCHID=beta/shh/1 ATIPSIG=$(licop-get-atip) make


Burning an ISO::

    wodim -verbose -data -eject \
        driveropts=burnfree \
        speed=4 \
        dev=/dev/cdrom \
        build/product.iso


